com.veraxsystems.vxipmi.coding.commands.sdr.record

Class DeviceRelativeEntityAssiciationRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.veraxsystems.vxipmi.coding.commands.sdr.record.SensorRecord
      • com.veraxsystems.vxipmi.coding.commands.sdr.record.DeviceRelativeEntityAssiciationRecord

  • public class DeviceRelativeEntityAssiciationRecord
extends SensorRecord
    This record is the same as the EntityAssociationRecord, except that it supports describing associations between entities that have device-relative Entity Instance values as well as system-relative values.
